多人入緊：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a7939c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=7ca871c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n不要說推<br />\n試著說812機場見"},{"pid":"2e569268b4c018ecbb67d246b5f8b65716e1df76","tid":1451191,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:17.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"bb4d38fe289a556cead0ef796689cdf78235b4eb","tid":1451191,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:43.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」"},{"pid":"55abae2f86948c5ae5efc331700d418a7509c0ce","tid":1451191,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a4ffbb31f69a275555e5320f965b4ac99cb4a1c3","tid":1451191,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:35:27.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"5f538915c0343a90c50e25eb9acd26b3e686fe48","tid":1451191,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:35:42.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"76e69180a88ccd5eef63a1e976b01bdfb8e4e0e3","tid":1451191,"uid":10125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:35:49.000Z","msg":"an eye for an eye"},{"pid":"528dcceadc53a3a3aad8c582336bdcdcfdda88d0","tid":1451191,"uid":216789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</s